Work-in-Progress / To-Do List:

1)  Fixing the above crashing issues.
2)  0Harmony integration and support.
3)  A modified IL2CPP Wrapper to be included with MelonLoader.
4)  An assembly generator for game specific Assembly DLL files.
5)  A Dependency Download system to automate installation of MelonLoader.
6)  A component based system for Mod loading and running.
7)  Support for games that use Mono instead of IL2CPP.